1/15/2013


 Goods and Services: 
Monitoring burglar and security alarms


 Mark Description: 
The mark consists of the word "FORWARD" in all capital letters, followed by two leftware pointing triangles, beneath which appear the words "HOME SECURITY" in all capital letters. The color black appears in the letters of "FORWARD". The color blue appears in the two triangles. The color gray appears in the letters of "HOME SECURITY".


 Type Of Mark: 
Service Mark


 Published For Opposition Date: 
10/30/2012


Last Applicant/Owner:

FORWARD HOME SECURITY, LLCPLANO, TX  75070
